  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add garlic and sauté until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add chicken and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add vinegar, soy sauce, bay leaves, black pepper, and salt. Stir to combine.",
    "Add water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20-25 minutes, or until the chicken is cooked through.",
    "Remove bay leaves and serve hot."
